NOTICE: THE CONTENT OF THIS README IS DEPRECATED!

Project Vaynwords 是一个用来从 twitter 收集单词的小工具。Project Vaynwords 是
自由软件，你可以随意使用，但用作商业目的的除外。

Project Vaynwords is a tool designed for collecting vocabulary from twitter.
Project Vaynwords is freeware, you can use it freely except in commercial.

---

作者： Vayn a.k.a VT <vt  at  elnode.com>

Author: Vayn a.k.a VT <vt  at  elnode.com>

---

特别感谢 Ryan Faerman 和他的 Twitter Search API。

Special thanks to Ryan Faerman and his Twitter Search
API.

---

System Requirement

>=PHP 5.2.6 with curl enabled
(It may work with most installations of PHP5, I don't test.)

---

如何安装？

1. 设置 config.php $vw_username 填写你的 twitter 账号$vw_hashtag 填写你设定的
hashtag (关于什么是 hashtag 请自行 Google 之)这两项*必填*。

2. 修改包括文件夹在内的所有文件的权限为 777使用 ftp 软件或 ssh 工具 (如果服务器
支持) 均可，具体方法请自行 Google。

3. 初始化程序用浏览器打开 check_update.php 即可.

4. 修改 check_update.php 的文件名请将 check_update.php 的名字修改为任意名称，并
且不要对他人透露。

5. 使用 cronjob 之类的自动化工具定时访问修改名称后的 check_update.php你可以使用
wget 或 curl 配合 cronjob 定时访问 check_update.php有关这方面的内容请自行查询，
定时访问时间建议最短不要小于 15 分钟。

How to install?

1. Set config.php
$vw_username is your twitter username
$vw_hashtag is your special hashtag (If you don't know what's hashtag,
please google it)
Both ofthem are *required*.

2. Change permission of all files and directories to 777
You can change permission with ftp software and ssh tools (If your server
supports)

3. Initialize
Use any kinds of broswers to visit check_update.php

4. Change file name of check_update.php
Please change file name of check_update.php to any string(except illegal
characters) you want, but don't expose it.

5. Catch check_update.php (which has been changed name) regularly
You can use cronjob and wget/curl or other software to catch the page.
Do not catch page too frequently.

---

如何使用？

把要记录的 单词+hashtag 发送到 twitter 即可 :)

How to use?

Send the word with hashtag to twiter, that's all. So easy~

